{
  "stem": "17308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 62.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To be quite candid, nobody had particular plans, because nobody expected things to go so bad-- turned much worse than expected.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And besides this, nobody had financial arrangements to go immediately further, because everything was left behind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the [INAUDIBLE] when it started in the morning, the banks opened-- was a mad rush.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People taking some money out, but nobody knew how much you had to take out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody was prepared for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in France, we eventually landed in Toulouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, stayed sometime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, Belgium was occupied, at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- didn't sound so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rumors were the German behaved well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did behave well at the begin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then eventually, my parents, my brother, and my-- another part of the family [INAUDIBLE], they went bank to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they left everything behind, and they were told things were right to settle matters They needed means, and everything was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- had to fix up matters at the factory, had to fix up the home arrangement, everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the news we could, that there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they left me, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remained Toulouse, at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was a British national.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A British citizen at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I'm South African.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then it was dangerous for me to go back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time I was 20-- 24.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had no particular plan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to get out of France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, [INAUDIBLE] I managed to get a visa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Military age was already a problem at the time, because military age, they were not allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German were controlling, already, France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the short time they controlled them, France was divided in what they call the Vichy area and occupied France.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
